SD.4 StructureDefinition-carin-rtpbc-OperationOutcome

title: StructureDefinition-carin-rtpbc-OperationOutcome-intro layout: default active: StructureDefinition-carin-rtpbc-OperationOutcome-intro â€”

This profile constrains the OperationOutcome resource for communicating situations when an exception prevents an insurer from returning a consumer real-time pharmacy benefit check response.
